PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779304272
OL,3,CDriver who fled scene of fatal crash
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FFollowing the incident Hussain fled
OL,7,Fthe scene and made two phone calls -
OL,8,Fone to a relative and one to the car's
OL,9,Fowner.
OL,11,FFootage showed he had been driving at
OL,12,Fspeeds of over 60mph in 30mph zones
OL,13,Fand was travelling at 49mph when he
OL,14,Fcrashed.
OL,16,FHussain later handed himself in to
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
