FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779304272
OL,3,CDriver who fled scene of fatal crash
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FHe admitted causing death and serious
OL,7,Finjury by dangerous driving, and
OL,8,Fdriving without insurance when he
OL,9,Fappeared at Sheffield Crown Court in
OL,10,FJanuary.
OL,12,FHe has now been jailed for five years
OL,13,Fand four months and banned rom driving
OL,14,Ffor seven years and eight months.
OL,16,FJudge Graham Steed KC told him he was
OL,17,F"young, immature and an inexperienced
OL,18,Fdriver behind the wheel of a powerful
OL,19,Fcar".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
