PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779304272
OL,3,CDriver who fled scene of fatal crash
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"Whether you were showing off or
OL,7,Fincapable, your standards were below
OL,8,Fthat of a responsible driver," he
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,F"No amount of sentence will put a
OL,12,Fvalue on Mohammed Waheed's life, but
OL,13,Fit needs to put punishment on you for
OL,14,Fhis death."
OL,16,FSgt John Taylo, of South Yorkshire
OL,17,FPolice, said: "While this will never
OL,18,Fundo the death and destruction caused
OL,19,Fby his actions, justice for Mohammed
OL,20,Fand his family has been achieved.
